rows.label: tlk43100246_03_msg0001
rows.name:
We've been kinda hard up for stuff
lately.

rows.label: tlk43100246_03_msg0002
rows.name: All we get to eat is Puran...

rows.label: tlk43100246_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I tell you what, I'd love to eat a
bucketload of that Fleur Bavarian.

rows.label: tlk43100246_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I bet posh folks have a bucket of it
for every meal.

rows.label: tlk43100246_03_msg0005
rows.name:
If I could catch a Speckled Whalefish,
well, I'd be rich, too!

rows.label: tlk43100246_03_msg0006
rows.name:
That'd be the end of government
rations for me!

rows.label: tlk43100246_03_msg0007
rows.name: But all I ever catch is Bipedal Crabs...
